replies.body:
Favourite stroke:  Free, Breast
Most Hated:  Back (Gets water in your nose :c)
Favourite Drill:  "cow" xD Its basically Fly Mixed with under over x3
How many times a week I practice: 5/7 (all weekdays ;-;)
Best 50 free: 24.50 (Im in gold :P)
Best 50 fly: 29.64 (Again, in gold :P)
Do you have morning practice: No, but I do practice 2 hours after school ;-;

Btw, Im on an Actual kind of... official  team, that participates in tourneys and such :P
